# =================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =================================================================
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT SECURITY REQUIREMENTS:
#
# 1. NEVER commit this .env file to version control
# 2. Use different keys for staging/production
# 3. Rotate the SERVICE_ROLE_KEY regularly
# 4. Keep API keys secret and never expose in frontend
# 5. Use environment-specific values for each deployment
#
# =================================================================
# VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
# =================================================================
# Before deploying, verify these are set correctly:
# ✅ APP_URL matches your deployment domain
# ✅ VITE_SUPABASE_URL is your Supabase project URL
# ✅ VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY is valid and not expired
# ✅ VITE_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY is newly generated (not the old hardcoded one!)
# ✅ OPENROUTER_API_KEY has credits and is active
# ✅ GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD is valid (not regular password)
# ✅ All values are for the correct environment (staging/prod)